Execution
------------
Once this sdk-constructor.tar.gz file had been unpacked take into account the following
steps in order to create prodfs folder and image creation.

1. Untar toolchain.tar.gz in the directory indicated above.
2. Untar otp-host.tar.gz tar tar file in the directory indicated above.
3. Untar sdk.tar.gz in the directory indicated above.
4. Once in the top directory, execute "bash .launchers/linux/sdk/install-prodfs-sdk"
    This will execute the following:
        *Source all environment variables (env-plf-config, env-buildsys-static, env-common, env-static).
        *"prodfs" folder will be created in .build
        *"2K" folder will be created in release/images/devel
        *"log" folder will be populated
5. You will find the images created in release/images/devel/2K/
